ChangelogDescription:
**New Features**

*• Trade system, trade Items & Pokemons with other players! [ALPHA]*
*• Changelog system, view our latest updates easier!*
*• Gift system, gift someone Poketokens or Pokecoins!*
*• Item system, use items or gift items to players!*

**Coming Soon**

*• Work to language control, soon able to choose your prefered Guild language!*
